import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { Box,Button,FormLabel,TextField } from '@mui/material'
const AddBook = () => {
  const [inputs,setInputs] = useState({
    Name:'',
    Description:'',
    Price


  })
  return (
    <form >
      <Box display='flex'flexDirection="column" justifyContent={'center'} maxWidth='700' alignContent={'center'} alignSelf='center' mr={'auto'} marginTop='10'>
      <FormLabel>Name</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='normal' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Name'/>
<FormLabel>Author</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='Author' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Author'/>
<FormLabel>Description</FormLabel>
<TextField margin='Description' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Description'/>
<FormLabel >Price</FormLabel>
<TextField type={'number'} margin='normal' fullWidth variant='outlined'name='Price'/>
      <Button type='submit' variant='contained'></Button>
      </Box>
      
    </form>
  )
}

export default AddBook
